name: Exploration Ball VII
description:
The seventh piece of a series about " The Exploration Ball ". This spherical entity is present in a certain amount of my artworks. Illustrating my own soul getting lost in the large worlds. Flying around the empty spaces of the universe, floating and exploring, this sphere can have a different structure inside.

Special unique 1/1 piece, animated and with sound. 

MP4 file - 1236 x 2304

Exploration Ball VII - Life
